data.description: PERRY HOMES NEW CONSTRUCTION! Home office with French doors set along one side of two-story entry. Kitchen and dining area open to two-story family room. Kitchen features corner walk-in pantry and generous island with built-in seating space. Two-story family room features wall of windows and a wood mantel fireplace. First-floor primary suite includes bedroom with 10-foot ceiling. Double doors lead to primary bath with dual vanities, garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower and large walk-in closet. First-floor guest suite offers private bath. Game room and two secondary bedrooms are upstairs. Extended covered backyard patio. Mud room off three-car garage.
